    <item>
      <title>沙特阿拉伯将成为全球最大的建筑市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/saudi-arabia-set-to-become-world-s-biggest-construction-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[房地产咨询集团莱坊表示，随着沙特阿拉伯向旨在改革和多元化经济的项目投入大量资金，沙特阿拉伯将成为全球最大的建筑市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/saudi-arabia-set-to-become-world-s-biggest-construction-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 04:06:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国总理警告脱钩将导致“恶性循环”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/china-premier-warns-decoupling-will-lead-to-destructive-spiral</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国务院总理李强警告称，如果各国在经济上分道扬镳，将给世界带来负面影响，同时反驳有关中国产业政策导致产能过剩的批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/china-premier-warns-decoupling-will-lead-to-destructive-spiral</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 03:29:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国警告朝鲜边境有寄生虫，朝鲜向边境投放更多垃圾气球</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/north-korea-sends-more-trash-balloons-over-border-as-south-warns-of-parasites</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国政府称，在朝鲜之前的垃圾气球中检测到蛔虫等寄生虫后，朝鲜又向韩国境内派出了一批携带垃圾的气球。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/north-korea-sends-more-trash-balloons-over-border-as-south-warns-of-parasites</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 01:52:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞指责马克龙散布“内战”言论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/macron-says-extreme-opposition-parties-would-lead-to-civil-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玛丽娜·勒庞表示，法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙指责极右翼国民联盟和左翼联盟的议程可能导致“内战”，这表明他知道自己将输掉于周日开始的立法投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/macron-says-extreme-opposition-parties-would-lead-to-civil-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 18:14:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非各政党接近就内阁职位达成一致</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/south-african-political-parties-nearing-accord-on-cabinet-posts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，南非两个最大政党即将就各自部长人数达成一致，以便与其他小党派组建广泛的联合政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/south-african-political-parties-nearing-accord-on-cabinet-posts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 15:16:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
